Same error here.

I think this is a regression of onnxruntime 1.13

The `setup.py` now depends on 3rd party package `packaging`, without declaring the dependency.   I believe it should be specified in `pyproject.toml`:

```toml
[build-system]
requires = ["packaging"]
```
